# TechNova AI Customer Support Agent

An intelligent, fully automated customer support system built with n8n, Google Gemini AI, Gmail, and Google Sheets. This workflow automatically reads incoming customer emails, searches a knowledge base, generates a professional AI-written reply, and sends it back to the customer without any human intervention.

---

## What This Project Does

When a customer sends an email, this automation:

1. Detects the new email via Gmail Trigger
2. Loads all FAQ entries from a Google Sheets knowledge base
3. Uses a JavaScript keyword matching algorithm to find the most relevant answer
4. Sends the matched answer to Google Gemini AI to write a warm, professional reply
5. Automatically sends the reply back to the customer via Gmail

---

## Tools and Technologies Used

- **n8n** (Self-hosted, v2.19.4) — workflow automation platform
- **Gmail Trigger** — detects incoming customer emails
- **Google Sheets** — stores the knowledge base (FAQ entries)
- **JavaScript Code Node** — keyword scoring algorithm for answer matching
- **Google Gemini AI** (models/gemini-3-flash-preview) — generates professional email replies
- **Gmail** — sends the automated reply to the customer

