## How the Keyword Matching Works

The JavaScript Code node:

- Combines the email subject and body into one text string
- Loops through every row in the knowledge base
- Scores each FAQ question by counting how many keywords from the question appear in the email
- Returns the highest scoring match as the best answer
- Falls back to a default message if no match is found

